        <p MadCap:conditions="General.Online-Only">To receive a notification from Pulse, you must be subscribed to the feed where the status update was posted <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare">(see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Flare/Pulse/Moderation/Subscribing-Topics.htm">Subscribing to Communities and Topics</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Pulse">(see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Pulse/Moderation/Subscribing-Topics.htm">Subscribing to Communities and Topics</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText>. You must also enable the appropriate Pulse feature in the Notifications tab on the Settings page of your profile <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare">(see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Flare/Pulse/Getting-Started/Creating-Editing-Profiles.htm">Editing Your&#160;Profile</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Pulse">(see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Pulse/Getting-Started/Creating-Editing-Profiles.htm">Editing Your&#160;Profile</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText>.</p>
